{"tid":1628683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家Twitter 戰線繼續gogogo","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:06:00.000Z","uid":613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1d27233002ada952672109ee3ea6ccadf9ddb0","tid":1628683,"uid":613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:10:50.000Z","msg":"1. 加呢個tg bot<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0hYeR4s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hYeR4s.png&h=bbb7fa7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 入指令攞任務<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hi8izib.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHi8izib.png&h=697ce898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文唔錯嘅，就寫個tweet<br />\nlike 個tweet, comment 左佢先，再retweet with comment <br />\n<br />\n就算英文麻麻地，都可以用d 熱門d 嘅hashtag retweet 左佢先。 我就鐵膽#standwithhk #standwithhongkong #liberatehongkong 呢d<br />\n<br />\n如果玩twitter 嘅人同出去嘅人差不多，一定有好強效果。<br />\n<br />\n依家香港人權及民主法案入緊大直路，我地twitter 戰線一定要GO GO GO<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n天滅中共，全黨死清光！！！！"},{"pid":"d2671cbd76996d096b0d3e8562772fee781b98ed","tid":1628683,"uid":291465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ab44a08ffb54fdc487ed799b34cb87b6637f8a","tid":1628683,"uid":613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2671cbd76996d096b0d3e8562772fee781b98ed","tid":1628683,"uid":291465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"可能比3毛舉報"},{"pid":"adeb669a007d2578f0f20dd71b68f09dc3580024","tid":1628683,"uid":613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1df84775b05983a0f1e15fd550e704de1583d750